NUMBER 1444
REGION 4
WASTE
CHANNEL 85
NAME Death Mountain, Fortress
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand at the mist-choked peak of Death Mountain. At the summit, the sun
appears several times larger than at the bottom. You stand in the shadow of
a twisted fortress constructed right at the mountain-top, profiled by the
eerie light. The structure was made with no logic whatsoever; towers jut
out at bizarre, insane angles. Windows appear at random location. Curtain
walls stand crooked, sloping up and down in nonsensical directions.
The gate itself lacks any sort of defenses, and its heavy doors have
been thrown wide open.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 1230 VAL2=999
ITEM 1 65 VAL2=1445 OPEN UNLOCKED
IFPREVERB GO 0
	ECHO PLAYER You jump into the mist and emerge back on the mountain trail.
	ECHO OTHERS Suddenly, %N leaps into the mist and vanishes!
	MOVE 999
	AFFECT 999
	ECHO OTHERS %N jumps out of the mist!
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
