NAME Fortress of Chaos, Balconies
REGION 4
CHANNEL 85
INDOOR_FLOOR
MONSTER_GROUP 99
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are standing in a balcony far over a bizarre scene. At least a hundred
feet below you, the assembled princes of chaos hold court. Gibbering masses
of tentacled flesh and and slimy, amorphous forms cackle and shout at one
another in half-bestial tones of anarchy. Gargoylish demons, servitor-fiends
and other perverse abominations dance erratically about their lords in a
grand, decadent display of feigned obedience, whilst others prattle, giggle,
howl, moan, laugh, sneer and roar in a mockery of every law ever created by
man or god. A filth-covered stairway leads down amidst the madness.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 1446
