REGION 4
CHANNEL 85
MONSTER_GROUP 98
INDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This high-vaulted chamber is the center of a number of mazelike passages. The various halls wend through the fortress at odd angles, some sloping upwards at harsh degrees, others slanting sideways to force uneven footing. The floor is checkered black and white, and reminds you of some sort of asylum. A single, narrow door is on the east side of the room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 66 VAL1=10 VAL2=1458
EXIT NE 1454
EXIT SW 1451
EXIT N 1453
EXIT D 1454
EXIT W 1455
;
NUMBER 1456
NAME Tower of Anarchy, Bottom
REGION 4
CHANNEL 85
INDOOR_FLOOR
MONSTER_GROUP 99
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
A crooked stairway leads more or less up into the tower. As you watch it the steps move around as each one refuses to line up with its neighbor above and below. There are no right angles of even straight line in this place. That it maintains its structural integrity at all defies all reason.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 66 VAL1=75 VAL2=1452
EXIT U 1457
;
NUMBER 1457
NAME Tower of Anarchy, Center
REGION 4
CHANNEL 85
MONSTER_GROUP 99
INDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Crazy shaped bricks of all sizes have been stacked to gether with purple goo to form walls. A shuddering, twisting stairway spirals away in both directions. As you look at it, the stair moves slightly. That the stairway will eventually take you up, is the only rule it follows.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT D 1456
EXIT U 1461
