NUMBER 1433
NAME Centrex
REGION 4
MONSTER_GROUP 96
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 85
WASTE
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The deep orange sky, streaked with swathes of purple clouds, stretches from horizon to horizon overhead. This is met by the featureless red sands that extend out from your position. The flaming amber sun roils, sending fingers of searing heat toward the desolate plain. A single mountain breaks the monotony to the east, and canyon walls rise up from the desert floor to create a pass to the west.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 1432
EXIT S 1440
EXIT E 1439
EXIT W 1434
IFPREVERB EAST -1
	PLREVENT
	CONTPLREVENT
	ECHO ALL As you travel eastward, the mountain seems to move further away.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB WEST -1
	PLREVENT
	CONTPLREVENT
	ECHO ALL As you travel westward, the mountain seems to move closer.
ENDIF
;
