NUMBER 3260
NAME Hell's backflow
REGION 0
CHANNEL 111
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Flames burn in the corners of this chamber and make it uncomfortably
hot. The light is just bright enough to make out the demons that arrive
to teach you a lesson or two. Waves of some sort of mental energy leech
into your brain and make it impossible to concentrate. There is a way
out, but you aren't sure you could make it if you tried.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
OUTOFBODY
EXIT O 3260
IFPREVERB O -1
  CLEARVERB
  RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
  IFVAR DUMMY1 ! 1
    ECHO PLAYER The way out moves! You must try again!
    ECHO OTHERS %N lunges for the way out, but misses.
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 2
    ECHO PLAYER [Round: 2 Sec]
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You made it out!
    MOVE PBACKFLOW
    AFFECT PBACKFLOW
    ECHO OTHERS %N arrives, looking very nervous.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CAST -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't concentrate enough to do that.
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks frustrated.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PROJECT -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't concentrate enough to do that.
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks frustrated.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't concentrate enough to do that.
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks frustrated.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB ATTACK -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't concentrate enough to do that.
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks frustrated.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB BACKSTAB -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't concentrate enough to do that.
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks frustrated.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB HIDE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't concentrate enough to do that.
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks frustrated.
ENDIF
