NUMBER 2225
NAME Eternal agony of torment
REGION 0
CHANNEL 112
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You find yourself in a black void. Screams of agony fill your ears, but
you can't see the sources of the sound. You are floating wildy out of
control and are very disoriented. There is a way out that you can see.
Something tells you take making for this exit is what you are expected
to do.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ASTRAL
DARKNESS
OUTOFBODY
EXIT O 3261
IFPREVERB O -1
  CLEARVERB
  RANDOM DUMMY2 1 100 0
  IFVAR DUMMY2 ! 1
    IFVAR RAC < 7
      ECHO PLAYER Before you can make it out, pain slams you back.
      ECHO OTHERS %N WRITHES IN AGONY.
      SPELL 314 30
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER Fire appears from nowhere to burn you!
      ECHO PLAYER You missed the exit this try.
      ECHO OTHERS Fire appears from out of nowhere to burn %N
      SPELL 117 30
    ENDIF
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You made it out!
    ECHO OTHERS %N escapes!
    MOVE PAGONY
    AFFECT PAGONY
    ECHO OTHERS %N arrives, but does not look too well.
  ENDIF
ENDIf
